  94:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) RxFifoFullCallback        : Rx Fifo Full Callback.
  95:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) TxFifoEmptyCallback       : Tx Fifo Empty Callback.
  96:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) MspInitCallback           : USART MspInit.
