 234:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****              in the data register is transmitted but is changed by the parity bit.
 235:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) USART polarity
 236:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) USART phase
